# Cribl sample events live here. Each .json file is a Cribl-formatted sample
# (typically a list of {"_raw": "..."} objects, optionally with structured fields).
#
# These files are referenced by default/samples.yml and surfaced in Cribl's UI
# "Sample Data" preview pane. They can also be reused as test fixture inputs
# (copy or symlink into tests/fixtures/<pipeline>/).
